<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>SUNPARNAK RAM I VANMI HNA CH94</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Sunparnak ram i vanmi hna, Leiah nan thla run zam u, Sernak kong a rak
 chimtu hna, Messiah chuahnak kong chim u.

[C1]
   Ra law, bia u, Ra law, bia u, Bawi Khrih Siangpahrang chuak thar.

[V2]
 Fing le tlang le tlimno rawn ah, Zan i tuu a cawngmi hna, Mi sinah
 Pathian a um cang, Vawlei Ceunak a ra cang.

[C2]
   Ra law, bia u, Ra law, bia u, Bawi Khrih Siangpahrang chuak thar.

[V3]
 Tinfim hna, nan khuaruah bang u, Ceunak hlapi ah a tlang, Phun kip
 duhmi cu kawl cio u, A chuah arfi nan hmuh cang.

[C3]
   Ra law, bia u, Ra law, bia u, Bawi Khrih Siangpahrang chuak thar.

[V4]
 Biaktheng hmai i a kun mithiang, Kum saupi a ngangmi hna, Bawipa cu a
 rung tum cang i, Biakinn chungah a lang lai, Ra law, bia u, Ra law, bia
 u. Bawi Khrih Siangpahrang chuak thar.

[C4]
   Ra law, bia u, Ra law, bia u, Bawi Khrih Siangpahrang chuak thar.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<hymn_number>94</hymn_number>
</song>